data.description: Don't miss your chance to view this affordable, thoughtfully developed horse property in Union! Uncover the charm of a well-maintained 2-bed, 2-bath single level home. Situated on over an acre, 1611 West Arch St. boasts a new roof along with a workshop, barn, cross-fenced area for horses, round pen, two indoor stalls, hay cover, outdoor storage shed, water rights from Red Mill Ditch and unobstructed mountain views. Enjoy the convenience of modern updates while surrounded by the beauty of the outdoors. Call today for a tour before it's gone!
